rComments: Prof. Dallesasse  is a rare combination (sadly) for an engineering professor of someone who has a genuine desire to disseminate his knowledge and who has spent time in industry to make real contributions and know what is important. Crystal clear explanationschallenging questions and a wealth of knowledge and experience. Need more like him.
EFFECTIVELY a nice, formal professor with a great background in ECE (EFFECTIVELY Semiconductors and Lasers). EFFECTIVE in teaching but can get a little boring in class.
